2.1 Kano World is a hosting service. Users of Kano World may submit, upload and post audio, text, photos, videos, pictures, comments, and other data or information (“Content”), which will be stored by Kano at the direction of such users, and may be shared and distributed by Kano with you and other users of Kano World using the tools and features provided as part of Kano World. Kano World also enables you to interact with one another, and enables any user of Kano World to view, comment on and share Content uploaded and made available on Kano World.

2.2 We may, from time to time, release new tools and resources on Kano World or introduce other services and/or features for Kano World. Any new services and features will be subject to this agreement as well as any addition terms of use that we may release for those specific services or features.

