5.1 You are not obliged to register to use Kano World. However, parts of Kano World are only available to registered users.

5.2 If you are under 13 years of age, you may only use Kano World if: (i) you provide us with a parent’s, legal guardians’, or teacher’s (as applicable) valid email address; and (ii) your account is validated by your parent, legal guardian, or teacher within 14 days.  If you are 13 years of age or more, but less than 16 years of age you may use Kano World only if you have obtained your parent(s)’ or legal guardian(s)’ permission.

